{"tid":204983,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"迪迪尼一日遊分享","createTime":"2017-04-17T12:38:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T05:01:49.000Z","uid":19068,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d447638e58336a267874ebb89cbf77d4d34208cf","tid":204983,"uid":19068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T12:38:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/17/203332_ac5fcb60128d8d8055723fff3f6b508e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F17%2F203332_ac5fcb60128d8d8055723fff3f6b508e.jpg&h=72970abe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/17/203334_aabf0c0360698afceee88546ab2457e7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F17%2F203334_aabf0c0360698afceee88546ab2457e7.jpg&h=1902288e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CrHjUsT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCrHjUsT.jpg&h=71a5efaf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2yv201s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2yv201s.jpg&h=ea7054be&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oR0g237.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoR0g237.jpg&h=7f554cf4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/386C43k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F386C43k.jpg&h=90e86547&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n十幾廿年冇去迪迪尼，依然感覺夢幻。<br />\n<br />\n利伸 好耐冇揸機，純分享<br />\n用緊nikon d7200，手機app執相，趁d7200再跌價前影多幾張，當年買左成萬蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b0963b55cf7bd906d8aa733f4d378aeee8fc6f5","tid":204983,"uid":44423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T12:45:23.000Z","msg":"唐老鴨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"288b93ed74888b235e2019acc93d5edc5ba90fc8","tid":204983,"uid":19068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T12:49:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唐老鴨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我本身扮到米奇同唐老鴨把聲，諗住係啲店到拎住兩隻公仔扮佢地講野拍片，結果太毒唔敢拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef73fc94333560ee6537dfa00f9739f104c011f5","tid":204983,"uid":3037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T12:58:43.000Z","msg":"最尾果兩張邊個位影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da4ece3b3a4c19a5b7eaad7f549a219c229df98e","tid":204983,"uid":19068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:09:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最尾果兩張邊個位影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有個位叫童話花園，入去之前以為迷官咁。"},{"pid":"82f62f06b47b206f798a10f0079aff061e044f24","tid":204983,"uid":68478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:15:01.000Z","msg":"好夢幻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打有冇買年票"},{"pid":"d0ab2d1ae76272f0a0d1c73c6db342c74636fbe8","tid":204983,"uid":19068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:27:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好夢幻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打有冇買年票</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁啱同frd有飛去加上自己想睇下ironman"},{"pid":"c4d12b5e1bca43e42b23531892e2d52bb86d6445","tid":204983,"uid":24775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:29:34.000Z","msg":"好靚啊影得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca43b48