56e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇左4d，另外個排隊入嘅展冇睇到，應該個到多嘢影。<br />\n啲相未執，大景相又生疏哂，依家返到屋企附近食緊晚餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc402013f065ac960847932fb643e1a11cb23112","tid":204983,"uid":19068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:50:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好靚啊影得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nthx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa96141efe09b262be56e99a079331398213ed8f","tid":204983,"uid":25052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:52:21.000Z","msg":"影得好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec0d24188cae4ae532ca36470a7d70cf5de7fd69","tid":204983,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:54:44.000Z","msg":"好靚喎影得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da50dc9284178c6c3627a18a672dc61863323201","tid":204983,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:56:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oR0g237.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoR0g237.jpg&h=7f554cf4&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsuperb!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7770440c56cc6906d79dafacbba1ce0a7f12882","tid":204983,"uid":19068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:57:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>影得好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nthx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4b09eceaca9b76067a9f6d35ff878e4e3d1738b","tid":204983,"uid":19068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:57:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好靚喎影得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nthx <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2c54f4f1317b19fd329a70a75d35838b56fde5f","tid":204983,"uid":40445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:59:49.000Z","msg":"用咗重曝?"},{"pid":"69ff20d0a73cc01ca209a5018515a2c51e83535f","tid":204983,"uid":40445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:00:07.000Z","msg":"用咗重曝? 幾靚"},{"pid":"96378e2a14f25ab29df71725236e6b7c353aee89","tid":204983,"uid":19068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:12:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用咗重曝? 幾靚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n相機開重曝驚miss左啲景，搵啲多燈位影定先，睇相覺得有match嘅就趁係入面坐低抖下時入落手機用app合成"},{"pid":"59fca9963fa6fbb041c5135ec57c27395777ef70","tid":204983,"uid":83935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T15:42:41.000Z","msg":"最尾個兩張點影 求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ab665924248517465bcbba833bab0e9be0c6c69","tid":204983,"uid":19068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T16:39:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最尾個兩張點影 求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n重曝效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n先對燈位out fo影一張<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m78GNg1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm78GNg1.jpg&h=08d364d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後影張主體<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RY3gMh8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRY3gMh8.jpg&h=dd4b065a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住我係iphone用photoshop mix合成<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/18/003943_39b89ca37b45c3e390c48d0906532f68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F18%2F003943_39b89ca37b45c3e390c48d0906532f68.jpg&h=3d147961&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n重曝係種效果，有啲相機有呢個功能可以即時合成，但係要連續影哂要合成嘅相。用app整就可以之後慢慢揀相玩"},{"pid":"ffa01c487206ddfaacfd76e98396057f99e19600","tid":204983,"uid":19068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T17:02:48.000Z","msg":"本身朝早先執，啲frd話要返人頭相，我忍唔住用iphone執住堆先<br />\n<br />\n同chewbacca 單獨合照要咁影，我差啲頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j8KzxB4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj8KzxB4.jpg&h=1f2f75cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<del><span style=\"font-size: small;\">相中人是我朋友，我朋友不是我</span></del><br />\n<br />\n呢個鬼佬勁呀，影之前的高屎忽，狗仔式轉呼拉圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過同小朋友玩得好埋<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b1Em6r4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb1Em6r4.jpg&h=6b5d9482&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/18/004935_15d5f4a468cce8dbdd410aa2072d6d94.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F18%2F004935_15d5f4a468cce8dbdd410aa2072d6d94.jpg&h=2bf121c1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/18/004936_be38a8dd8a5d0cc06e51d119d3cbfa48.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F18%2F004936_be38a8dd8a5d0cc06e51d119d3cbfa48.jpg&h=bbfaf0f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩張景<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e2zo7yZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe2zo7yZ.jpg&h=257d0552&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/22ZS99d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F22ZS99d.jpg&h=0de614d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到夜晚啲星球好靚<br />\n呢張即時轉applewatch wallpaper<br />\n其他星球相未入<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L4UUN88.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL4UUN88.jpg&h=17b114d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n靚靚鬼妹，笑得好charm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6FAK17K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6FAK17K.jpg&h=fcfb0a3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得呢舊嘢好fun，所以影低左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G7e39Z3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG7e39Z3.jpg&h=7261021f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n掃樹掃到出神入化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/18/005540_a48b49781f669fc2cd5ec9d40f703bb4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F18%2F005540_a48b49781f669fc2cd5ec9d40f703bb4.jpg&h=7c42acde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入迪士尼，要轉錶面<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UiA40Nd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUiA40Nd.jpg&h=6607f673&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d18ec202d59cdd3f1cc2c9cb59f6bda5d09db41a","tid":204983,"uid":40908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T17:11:34.000Z","msg":"迪迪尼真係幾多野影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ca7b9f45f9d3dd5509aeb88a1df975a9d77cea2","tid":204983,"uid":19068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T17:21:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>迪迪尼真係幾多野影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係，但係掛住玩同行嚟行去都嘥唔少腳力，入館玩嘢要將相機袋出袋入都幾煩。<br />\n太陽又猛，帶著疲倦的身軀 奔走很遠...... 冇乜影公園景經驗，唔是好識處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d429a2d1a514da391da164143f0020493430211","tid":204983,"uid":34069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T17:26:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>迪迪尼真係幾多野影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係，但係掛住玩同行嚟行去都嘥唔少腳力，入館玩嘢要將相機袋出袋入都幾煩。<br />\n太陽又猛，帶著疲倦的身軀 奔走很遠...... 冇乜影公園景經驗，唔是好識處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一日影相一日玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}